headline: Ingersoll Rand Schedules 2024 Sustainability Investor Call
summary: DAVIDSON, N.C., Dec. 10, 2024 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Ingersoll Rand Inc. (NYSE: IR), a global provider of mission-critical flow creation and life science and industrial solutions, will host its 2024 sustainability investor call on December 17, 2024, at 8:00 a.m. Eastern Time to discuss the company’s commitment and recent accomplishments to Lead Sustainably. To participate in the call, please dial +1-800-715-9871, domestically, or +1-646-307-1963, internationally, and use access code 5314346. A real
